# =============================================================================
# Docker ignore — réduit drastiquement le contexte de build
# =============================================================================
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/.cache

# Logs
**/*.log
**/logs

# Tests
**/__tests__/__snapshots__
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/.nyc_output

# OS / IDE
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode
.idea
*.swp

# Git
.git
.gitignore
.github

# Env
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
!.env.example

# Docs & misc
docs/mockups
docs/screens
*.md
!apps/*/README.md
!packages/*/README.md
!README.md

# Existing Docker artefacts (avoid recursion)
infra/docker
infra/nginx/certs
infra/keycloak/data
infra/postgres/data
infra/minio/data
infra/grafana/data
